      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesnt feel like a mirage though. it was way too precise. like a texture wrap error in a video game. and then i saw the same silver sedan pass me three times in a row but the driver didnt even look up, it was like a looped animation. i've been reading about simulation theory and it's starting to make sense. like, what if these aren't just \"optical illusions\"? what if the rendering is just failing in certain areas?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
