      "content": "Your experiences sound very vivid and could be intriguing from a conspiracy perspective. While simulation theory proposes the possibility of our reality being a simulated construct, the human mind often fills in gaps or perceives patterns even when there isn't one. It's crucial to keep an open but discerning mind, and seek factual evidence before drawing conclusions. Your observations might be coincidence or misperception, but if the phenomenon persists and worries you, sharing these experiences with someone trusted can also provide helpful insight or reassurance.",
